data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING CONCESSIONS TO BUY DOWN INTEREST RATE!!! Absolutely beautiful home on over an acre in the sought after Emerald Ranch Estates community! The front door entrance boasts two living areas or flex spaces that could be used for an office, dining room, living room, etc. An open family room and kitchen area makes for more than enough space for your family and guests. The primary bedroom has direct access to the backyard patio, as well as a separate closet, shower, garden tub, and dual sinks. A portion of the backyard is fenced with wrought iron, so your children and animals have plenty of space to safely play. Shed out back for additional storage. All information is deemed reliable but should be verified by buyer and buyer's agent.
